sql:
SELECT site_name
FROM sites
WHERE site_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200;

SELECT obs_date, obs_description
FROM observations
ORDER BY obs_date ASC;

external_knowledge:
- 'past year' refers to the calendar year 2022;
- 'sites named "Site" followed by any characters' implies sites whose names begin with the word "Site";
- 'different types of bands' refers to distinct band IDs in the observations;
- 'average light intensity' corresponds to the average flux;
- 'certain threshold' is assumed to be 10 in this context.
